<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xml:id="KR5c0057-en-4e06a22c" type="transl"><teiHeader><fileDesc><titleStmt><title>DRAFT</title><editor role="translator">Harbsmeier 2024</editor></titleStmt><publicationStmt><ab>published electronically as part of the TLS project at https://hxwd.org</ab><availability status="1"><ab>This work is in the public domain</ab></availability></publicationStmt><sourceDesc><bibl><title>DRAFT</title>Copenhagen, 2024</bibl><ab>Translation of <bibl corresp="#KR5c0057"><title xml:lang="och">老子</title></bibl> into <lang xml:lang="en">English</lang>.</ab></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><creation resp="#CH">Initially created: <date>2024-01-04T21:16:28.162+09:00</date> by CH</creation></profileDesc></teiHeader><text><body><div><head>Translated parts</head><p xml:id="KR5c0057-start"><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_010-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:20:17.666+09:00">In supporting your confused soul so as to maintain the Pristine Unity</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_010-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:21:00.461+09:00">are you capable of avoiding any separation from it?</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_011-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:22:45.355+09:00">have the one and only hub in common.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_014-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:28:50.003+09:00">These three (features by which the Way is named) cannot be reached by investigation,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_014-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:30:05.184+09:00">and therefore one merges them into the One Primordial Unit.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_014-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:30:23.637+09:00">As for that One Primordial Unit,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_014-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:31:26.136+09:00">is neither shiny above</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_014-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:32:30.323+09:00">nor murky below (contains no dyadic oppositions):</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_014-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:34:11.978+09:00">it is all intertwined within itself and cannot be captured by a name:</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_014-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:34:57.684+09:00">it reverts to where there are no things.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_022-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:38:42.528+09:00">Thus it is that the sage embraces the Primordial Unity</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_022-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:39:22.979+09:00">and becomes the structural model for everyone under the sun.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.15" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:41:53.515+09:00">And so the Way is great</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.16" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:41:59.597+09:00">Heaven is great,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.17" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:42:06.256+09:00">Earth is great,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.18" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:44:36.599+09:00">the king is likewise great.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.19" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:45:32.734+09:00">Within the realm there are these four great roles</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.20" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:46:13.565+09:00">and king (only) one of them.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.21" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:46:45.915+09:00">Man models himself on Earth,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.22" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:46:57.666+09:00">Earth models itself on Heaven,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.23" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:47:08.65+09:00">Heaven models itself on the Way,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_025-1a.24" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:47:36.82+09:00">and the Way models itself on what causes itself to be so.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_039-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:49:50.087+09:00">As for those who have attained to the Primordial Unit of the Way</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_039-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:50:25.502+09:00">Heaven attained to it so as to be(come) clear,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_039-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T22:10:00.979+09:00">Earth attained to it so as to be(come) steady,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_039-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:52:09.948+09:00">Spirits attain to it so as to be(come) supernaturally efficacious,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_039-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:53:57.697+09:00">Dales attain to it so as to be(come) replete,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_039-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:55:00.191+09:00">all manner of creatures attain to it so as to be(come) alive,</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_039-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T21:57:20.186+09:00">princes and kings attain to it so as to become the guides to everyone under the sun.</seg><seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_039-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-04T22:08:09.934+09:00">What brings all this to perfect completion is the Primordial Unit of the Way.</seg></p></div></body></text></TEI>